name: total-teleop-cargo-miss-lower
title: Total Teleop Cargo Missed (Lower)
description: Total number of cargo that missed the lower hub (and did not score in upper hub) during Teleop
function:
let failed = data.eventLog.filter((event) => (event.name === 'fail_port' && event.variables.hub === 'lower' && event.timeStamp > 15));
return failed.length;
